{"tid":591921,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"俄婦埃及紅海水中分娩　胎兒連臍帶抱出水","createTime":"2018-03-14T00:46:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-14T11:15:44.000Z","uid":28366,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"6c8601bc34c10f0b2a4369cc9e702b9dabb5d916","tid":591921,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T00:46:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/14/084228_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F14%2F084228_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=dc87e33c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">該名孕婦（左）彷彿剛游完泳似的走上沙灘，而其丈夫（右）和醫生（中）就與新生嬰上岸。</span><br />\n<br />\n一名俄羅斯孕婦日前在埃及鄰近紅海的得合（Dahab）旅遊時，刻意安排在海中作水中分娩，並由丈夫與一名事先安排好的醫生接生，全程被當地居民拍下。其中該名醫生被拍到抱着連着臍帶的新生嬰，而該名丈夫則拿着盛載胎盤的盤子上岸。 <br />\n<br />\n賽義德（Hadia Hosny El Said）當時於其叔叔公寓的露台目睹一切，並把過程拍下，於上周六（10日）上載至社交網分享。從照片可見，該名孕婦躺在海中分娩，醫生負責把胎兒接住，一旁的丈夫手拿橙色的盤子，放置胎盤和臍帶。而孕婦生產完後，就彷彿剛從海中游完泳般走上沙灘，與正在海灘等待、相信是她較年長的兒子會合。 <br />\n<br />\n水中分娩是一種在暖水中誕下胎兒的分娩方式，據指有不少母親認為此分娩方式能減輕分娩過程中的痛楚；亦有人指胎兒以此方式出生，一般會較於空氣中出生平靜和較少掙扎，但未有明確的統計證據顯示水中分娩對嬰兒的健康有好處。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/14/084426_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F14%2F084426_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=a504266e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">醫生抱着新生嬰上岸</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/14/084512_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F14%2F084512_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=cc9015e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">眾人與正在海灘等待的男童（左）會合</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20180314/mobile/bknint-20180314024253722-0314_17011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180314%2Fmobile%2Fbknint-20180314024253722-0314_17011_001.html&d=W%2BH%2FhQi2htBT%2FNrt%2BuYF%2FMPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=65005610\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20180314/mobile/bknint-20180314024253722-0314_17011_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"2ef70f02bc25df8da233b5b4666373d4cbb39103","tid":591921,"uid":32511,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T00:48:55.000Z","msg":"冇菌？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a054e506739e021e8d40307107592b6979b190a","tid":591921,"uid":44454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T00:50:19.000Z","msg":"摩西"},{"pid":"2c017b9ca375a999f273890111a82274deb6c2a2","tid":591921,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9a054e506739e021e8d40307107592b6979b190a","tid":591921,"uid":44454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T00:50:19.000Z","msg":"摩西"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T00:54:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4783018cb244d878cfbf137e96bfc2dd3cf94ce","tid":591921,"uid":19437,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T01:04:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72c574538f9cf6861b0c4d4814e8587e28538f94","tid":591921,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T01:35:36.000Z","msg":"戰鬥民族"},{"pid":"1f4280596448dc3769af9b895e9ced6ee3617525","tid":591921,"uid":17011,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T02:14:56.000Z","msg":"痴撚線 生完仔仲輕輕鬆鬆咁行上岸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4fd68e6346a32b3173428a9bece44722a273b7a","tid":591921,"uid":9217,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"reply